✅ 方案B（不用浏览器）：纯Python截“关键字下面内容”

如果你不想用 Playwright，其实更简单👇

🔹 直接提取关键字下面内容
# extract_keyword.py
KEYWORD = "ERROR"
OUTPUT_LINES = 10  # 往下取多少行

with open("test.log", "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    lines = f.readlines()

result = []
capture = False
count = 0

for line in lines:
    if KEYWORD in line:
        capture = True

    if capture:
        result.append(line)
        count += 1

    if count >= OUTPUT_LINES:
        break

# 写入新文件
with open("filtered.log", "w") as f:
    f.writelines(result)

print("✅ 已生成 filtered.log")
